headline: Franklin Templeton Canada Announces Investment Fund Updates, including Fee Reductions and Series Terminations
summary: Franklin Templeton Canada today announced updates and adjustments across a number of investment funds, including fee reductions, proposed investment objective changes and series terminations. Franklin Templeton Canada regularly reviews its investment offerings to ensure that its ETF and fund lineup remains competitive and positioned to meet the evolving needs of investors and advisors.

headline: LPLA Partners With Simplicity to Boost Insurance Arm & Advisor Support
summary: LPL Financial collaborates with Simplicity to overhaul its insurance platform, boost advisor support and expand growth across its vast wealth network.
